author: boston.com
title: Driver hits, kills pedestrian while parallel parking in Plymouth - Massachusetts news
text:
A woman hit and killed a pedestrian while parallel parking her car Wednesday in Plymouth, a Plymouth police spokesman told Boston.com. The victim, a 62-year-old man, died later Wednesday afternoon.
Police are investigating the crash.
